namespace ArithmeticHodge.Analysis.YoshidaEvenMomentTargets

/-!
# Candidate targets for the full even moment block

These exact rational boxes are discovery witnesses for `S_1, ..., S_199`
and `D_0, ..., D_199`.  Merely defining them makes no claim that they contain
the analytic moments.  The theorems below kernel-check the first 10 and 25
inflated Schur pivots and serve as scaling regressions for the eventual
checkpointed 200-stage certificate.

The full pivot proposition and both analytic enclosure packages remain
explicit obligations.  In particular, this module is not a finite-block
positivity theorem.
-/

